<h2 style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 35px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>Understanding Domain and Hosting</strong></strong></h2>
<h4 style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 24px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>What is a Domain?</strong></strong></h4>
<p style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;border: 0px;">A domain serves as the address of your website on the internet. It&rsquo;s the unique identifier that users type into their browsers to access your site. Think of it as your online storefront&rsquo;s address, making it easier for visitors to find and navigate your content.</p>
<h4 style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 24px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>What is Web Hosting?</strong></strong></h4>
<p style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;border: 0px;">Web hosting, on the other hand, refers to the service that stores your website&rsquo;s files and data, making it accessible to users worldwide. It&rsquo;s like renting space on a server to house your website&rsquo;s content, ensuring it&rsquo;s always available for viewing.</p>
<h3 style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 29px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>Importance of Having Your Domain and Hosting</strong></strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;border: 0px;">Owning your domain and hosting offers numerous benefits, including:</p>
<p style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>Professionalism:</strong></strong> Having a custom domain lends credibility to your website and brand.</p>
<p style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>Control:</strong></strong> With your hosting, you have full control over your website&rsquo;s content, design, and functionality.</p>
<p style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>Customization:</strong></strong> Personalize your website to reflect your unique style and brand identity.</p>
<p style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 17px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>Scalability:</strong></strong> Easily upgrade your hosting plan as your website grows, accommodating increased traffic and resource demands.</p>
<h4 style="text-align: start;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 24px;border: 0px;"><strong><strong>Ways to Get Free Domain and Hosting</strong></strong></h4>
